          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*. Based on the assignment of 26 detected",
                " decay chains, the production cross sections for the",
                " 3n, 4n and 5n evaporation channels of the reaction",
                " Cm-248(Mg-26,xn)Hs-274-x were evaluated at five beam",
                " energies.",
                " *By authors*.Half-life calculated from E(a) values of",
                " the most probable transitions using the formalism",
                " from A.Parkhomenko et.al(see Acta.Phys.Pol.B,V.36,",
                " p.3095,2005)"
              ]
            }
          ],
